{"TopicId":180916,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"NERV Problems in VAB","CreatedByName":"Aegolius13","CreatedById":165625,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-27T03:12:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Aegolius13","CreatedById":165625,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-27T03:12:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI noticed a couple new bugs with the NERV when building in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E (version 1.6).\u00A0 First, when I select the engine from the menu, it the model shows the exhaust plume (both before and after attaching it to a node).\u00A0 Second, even when I have ample liquid fuel, the stock delta-v readout shows zero.\u00A0 But once I launch, it looks like the readout works fine.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anyone else run across this problem? If it matters, this is on a no-mod install with Making History.\u00A0 (This install used to have mods, but I deleted them all and re-verified local files through Steam).\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OHara","CreatedById":162784,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-27T04:18:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShadowZone gives six steps to solve the problem, many involving Valve\u0027s system \u0027Steam\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1568307465\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/50533-15x-module-manager-311-november-12th-2018-its-dangerous-to-go-alone-take-those-cats-with-you/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3509300\u0026amp;embedComment=3509300\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022 style=\u0022height:312px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you \u003Cu\u003Edon\u0027t\u003C/u\u003E use Steam, the same symptoms might appear\u00A0on the first start after adding/removing a mod or mods,\u003Cbr\u003E\nand are solved by closing and restarting KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-12-31T03:23:11Z\u0022 title=\u002212/31/2018 03:23  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 31, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by OHara\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eclarify\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aegolius13","CreatedById":165625,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-29T03:58:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep, that worked.\u00A0 My Kerbals thank you for the slightly safer \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E working conditions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benur","CreatedById":189292,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-30T22:18:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223511741\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180916\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221545884300\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162784\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OHara\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn \u200E12\u200E/\u200E27\u200E/\u200E2018 at 5:18 AM, OHara said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed366747295\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/50533-15x-module-manager-311-november-12th-2018-its-dangerous-to-go-alone-take-those-cats-with-you/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3509300\u0026amp;embedComment=3509300\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022 style=\u0022height:313px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOutside of Steam, simply closing and restarting KSP is enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi there, same here, I\u0027m lucky for finding this before posting my problem :-) What do you mean by \u0022Outside of Steam\u0022? Should I close KSP, close Steam, then restart KSP?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMany thanks in advance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OHara","CreatedById":162784,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-31T03:18:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223513501\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180916\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221546208333\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022189292\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Benur\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Benur said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you mean by \u0022Outside of Steam\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI meant that if your KSP installation does not use Steam,\u003Cbr\u003E\nyou can skip the first four steps in the 6-step process from ShadowZone that I quoted above.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll edit above to clarify.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}